222
00:15:53,875 --> 00:15:55,083
- RIGHT.

223
00:16:04,791 --> 00:16:06,916
- ALL RIGHT,
IT'S TIME TO GO, EUREKA.

224
00:16:15,333 --> 00:16:19,208
- DON'T BEG.  DO IT YOURSELF
OR ELSE YOU WON'T GET ANYTHING.

225
00:16:19,291 --> 00:16:22,041
I REALLY HOPE YOU KNOW THAT
I BELIEVE IN YOU, GRAMPS.

226
00:16:22,125 --> 00:16:23,333
I BELIEVE IN YOU!

227
00:16:27,166 --> 00:16:28,666
- WHAT?  THAT THING.

228
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:31,750
COMING WITHOUT A BOARD?
ARE THEY MOCKING ME?

229
00:16:31,833 --> 00:16:34,750
IF YOU WANNA DIE THAT MUCH,
I'LL BE HAPPY TO KILL YOU.

230
00:16:34,833 --> 00:16:36,083
BASCUDE!

231
00:16:36,166 --> 00:16:39,666
- RENTON.
- IT'S GRAMPS!

232
00:16:51,833 --> 00:16:54,625
- WHAT WAS THAT?  STUFF LIKE
THAT IRRITATES ME.

233
00:17:18,583 --> 00:17:21,500
- WHAT WAS THAT JUST NOW?
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE?

234
00:17:21,583 --> 00:17:24,000
DID YOU GET IT?
- NO GOOD.  IT WAS TOO FAST.

235
00:17:24,083 --> 00:17:25,708
THE GUN SIGHT CAMERAS
COULDN'T KEEP UP WITH IT.

236
00:17:25,791 --> 00:17:29,916
- CAN IT BE THAT THE typeZERO
HAS ACTUALLY EVOLVED?

237
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:31,791
- Renton: AMAZING!

238
00:17:31,875 --> 00:17:34,250
THIS SPEC TWO IS JUST AMAZING.

239
00:17:34,333 --> 00:17:37,250
- LET'S GO, COME ON.

240
00:17:37,333 --> 00:17:40,708
- YEAH.
LET'S GO, TOGETHER.

241
00:17:47,708 --> 00:17:49,166
- A SEVEN SWELL?

242
00:17:49,250 --> 00:17:52,458
- NO, THIS IS MUCH MORE
BRILLIANT THAN THAT.

243
00:17:52,541 --> 00:17:55,666
THIS-- THIS IS THE REAL.

244
00:17:55,750 --> 00:17:59,500
- WHAT IS THAT?  THERE'S NO WAY
I'M EVER GONNA LET MYSELF LOSE

245
00:17:59,583 --> 00:18:01,916
TO SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

246
00:18:07,708 --> 00:18:10,833
DIE!  DIE!  DIE!
DIE AGAIN AND DIE AGAIN!

247
00:18:10,916 --> 00:18:12,208
( gasps )

248
00:18:15,666 --> 00:18:18,041
- ( screaming )

249
00:18:19,916 --> 00:18:22,125
- WHAT IS THIS?
WHAT'S GOING ON?

250
00:18:28,041 --> 00:18:31,750
NO.  NO.  NO.  NO.  NO!

251
00:18:44,458 --> 00:18:47,416
- ( crying )
- WHAT'S THE MATTER?

252
00:18:47,500 --> 00:18:49,625
- PLEASE.

253
00:18:49,708 --> 00:18:53,666
HOLD MY HAND.
HOLD MY HAND.

254
00:19:05,791 --> 00:19:08,708
- THE SIGNALS FOR THE ANTIBODY
CORALIANS ARE STARTING

255
00:19:08,791 --> 00:19:11,875
TO GO AWAY
AND ARE GETTING WEAKER.

256
00:19:11,958 --> 00:19:13,708
- AFTER WE RETRIEVE THE NIRVASH,

257
00:19:13,791 --> 00:19:15,750
TAKE THIS SHIP
TO WHERE THE ZONE EMERGED.

258
00:19:15,833 --> 00:19:18,041
PERHAPS THERE MIGHT
BE A FEW CIVILIANS

259
00:19:18,125 --> 00:19:21,125
WHO MANAGED TO SURVIVE.
- ROGER THAT.

260
00:19:29,708 --> 00:19:31,750
- ( whimpering )

261
00:19:31,833 --> 00:19:35,750
- ANEMONE, ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

262
00:19:35,833 --> 00:19:37,500
TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED
OUT THERE.

263
00:19:37,583 --> 00:19:38,916
- Woman:
WE TOLD YOU TO GIVE PRIORITY

264
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:41,750
TO THE OBSERVATION
OF THE ANTIBODY CORALIANS.

265
00:19:41,833 --> 00:19:43,875
I MUST REPORT THIS INCIDENT
TO THE COLONEL.

266
00:19:43,958 --> 00:19:47,458
- WHAT?  IF WE LEAVE THE GEKKO
ALONE, SOMEDAY IT'LL PROVE

267
00:19:47,541 --> 00:19:50,875
TO BE AN ENORMOUS THREAT
TO US.  NOW WE CAN CRUSH IT.

268
00:19:50,958 --> 00:19:53,750
- WHAT CAN YOU EXPECT A MERE
BUNCH OF PIRATES TO DO NOW?

269
00:19:53,833 --> 00:19:55,875
THE WILL OF OUR GALLANT COLONEL

270
00:19:55,958 --> 00:19:58,625
IS AS BIG AS
THIS PLANET ITSELF.

271
00:19:58,708 --> 00:20:00,208
- ( whimpering )

272
00:20:03,208 --> 00:20:05,333
- HELLO, NIRVASH.

273
00:20:09,708 --> 00:20:11,791
- RENTON.

274
00:20:11,875 --> 00:20:14,791
I SEE HIS INTEGRITY HASN'T
CHANGED ONE BIT.

275
00:20:14,875 --> 00:20:16,916
- WHAT?

276
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:19,958
A SHIPPING STATEMENT?
WHY ME?

277
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:28,916
IT'S FROM GRAMPS.

278
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:32,916
- Axel: GREETINGS.  FIRST
OF ALL, ARE YOU DOING WELL?

279
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:35,916
THE TOWN YOU WERE BORN IS
WEARING A VEIL OF SNOW

280
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:39,916
WAITING EAGERLY FOR THE ARRIVAL
OF VIBRANT SPRING.

281
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:42,958
SINCE YOU LEFT HERE, YOU HAVEN'T
SENT ME A SINGLE LETTER.

282
00:20:43,041 --> 00:20:46,708
IF YOU HAD RETURNED
WITH EVERYTHING UP IN THE AIR,

283
00:20:46,791 --> 00:20:48,875
I WAS CONSIDERING PUNCHING
YOUR LIGHTS OUT.

284
00:20:48,958 --> 00:20:51,208
BUT IF YOU STILL HAVEN'T
FOUND YOUR ANSWERS,

285
00:20:51,291 --> 00:20:53,500
THAT'S FINE AS WELL.

286
00:20:53,583 --> 00:20:55,666
THE CURRENT SITUATION
HAS CREATED A NEED

287
00:20:55,750 --> 00:20:58,125
FOR ME TO GET OUT
OF TOWN AS WELL.

288
00:20:58,208 --> 00:21:01,750
FOR A WHILE, I'LL LOUNGE AROUND
WHERE I CAN STAY OUT OF SIGHT,

289
00:21:01,833 --> 00:21:05,333
BUT SOMEDAY I PROMISE I WILL
RETURN TO BELLFOREST.

290
00:21:05,416 --> 00:21:07,833
I WILL RETURN AND WAIT
AS LONG AS I CAN FOR YOU

291
00:21:07,916 --> 00:21:10,583
TO COME BACK TO THE PLACE
WE CALLED HOME.

292
00:21:10,666 --> 00:21:14,416
OH, AND BRING THAT
NICE YOUNG LADY.

293
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:16,833
- ( sniffling )

294
00:21:18,083 --> 00:21:20,500
- Man:
A CORALIAN AND A HUMAN.

295
00:21:20,583 --> 00:21:24,375
- IT'S ALMOST LIKE A FAIRY TALE.

296
00:21:24,458 --> 00:21:27,041
- Woman: THE ZERO NUMBER TWO'S
TEST LAUNCH WAS A SUCCESS.

297
00:21:27,125 --> 00:21:29,041
THE ANTIBODY CORALIANS APPEARED

298
00:21:29,125 --> 00:21:32,250
180 KILOMETERS NORTH
OF THE ORANGE IMPACT POINT.

299
00:21:32,333 --> 00:21:36,083
JUST LIKE ZERO ONE, THE TARGET'S
ACTIVITY AREA IS WITHIN

300
00:21:36,166 --> 00:21:39,541
THE RADIUS OF THE KUTE-CLASS
THAT APPEARED WITH IT.

301
00:21:39,625 --> 00:21:43,041
OH, YES, AND THERE SEEMS TO BE
A LIMIT TO ITS ACTIVITY TIME.

302
00:21:43,125 --> 00:21:46,041
- I SEE.
A VERY INTERESTING NUMBER.

303
00:21:46,125 --> 00:21:50,083
1,246 SECONDS--
RECOGNIZE IT?

304
00:21:50,166 --> 00:21:53,041
- YES, IT'S EXACTLY
THE SAME SPAN OF TIME

305
00:21:53,125 --> 00:21:56,083
AS THE SEVEN SWELL EFFECT
TRIGGERED BY typeZERO.

306
00:21:58,166 --> 00:22:01,375
- THE TIME HAS COME.
I WILL REMOVE THE "ZERO" TAG

307
00:22:01,458 --> 00:22:04,708
FROM THE ORANGES.
CONTINUE WITH THE STIMULATIONS,

308
00:22:04,791 --> 00:22:06,666
GATHER UP AS MUCH DATA
ON THE BEHAVIOR

309
00:22:06,750 --> 00:22:09,083
OF ANTIBODY CORALIAN
APPEARANCE POINTS AS YOU CAN.

310
00:22:09,166 --> 00:22:12,375
ONCE WE HAVE THAT, WE CAN MOVE
AGAINST THEIR CENTRAL CORE.

311
00:22:12,458 --> 00:22:15,333
NOW LET'S BEGIN.

